    transliterasi: "man 'amila sayyi`atan fa lā yujzā illā miṡlahā, wa man 'amila ṣāliḥam min żakarin au unṡā wa huwa mu`minun fa ulā`ika yadkhulụnal-jannata yurzaqụna fīhā bigairi ḥisāb",
